	>  5-
	>  6-
	>  7-

	$ quilt diff | grep -v "^\\(---\\|+++\\)"
	> Index: d/one.txt
	> ===================================================================
	> @@ -1,7 +1,7 @@
	>  1-
	>  2-
	>  3-
